598
00:52:36,834 --> 00:52:38,167
I'll leave the money here.

599
00:52:38,167 --> 00:52:40,000
I need to find my son.
I'm really sorry about this.

600
00:52:40,375 --> 00:52:42,083
You can buy a new phone.

601
