Are you crazy?
Come back here!

602
00:52:44,792 --> 00:52:47,375
Hey, buddy!

603
00:52:48,250 --> 00:52:49,751
Stop! Stop!

604
00:52:49,751 --> 00:52:52,000
Come back here!
Come back here, young man!

605
00:52:55,209 --> 00:52:57,209
Help me! Help me!
Help me!

606
00:52:57,959 --> 00:52:59,667
Come back here!
That's my phone!

607
00:53:00,876 --> 00:53:02,292
Stop! Stop!

608
00:53:40,292 --> 00:53:42,501
- Hello, Theo?
- He's OK, Branca.

609
00:53:42,542 --> 00:53:44,751
He's OK. Believe me...

610
00:53:44,751 --> 00:53:47,626
- He crossed a river.
