611
00:53:47,626 --> 00:53:49,459
A river... in a mangrove...

612
00:53:49,501 --> 00:53:51,417
He crossed on a ferry.
I talked to the owner of the ferry.

613
00:53:51,417 --> 00:53:53,667
They guy told me that he talked to him,
he had money and he was alright.

614
00:53:53,709 --> 00:53:55,542
He wanted to
buy the guy's cap.

615
00:53:55,792 --> 00:53:57,000
- And he's alright?
- Branca,

616
00:53:57,000 --> 00:53:59,459
I've met two people
who have talked to Pedro already.

617
00:53:59,459 --> 00:54:02,209
He traded his T-shirt...
He's fine. He's getting along.

618
00:54:02,876 --> 00:54:05,000
Find him for me.
Bring him home.

619
00:54:05,042 --> 00:54:06,501
I'm going to take him
home today.

620
00:54:06,501 --> 00:54:08,542
I'm getting close.
I'm real close now.

621
00:54:08,792 --> 00:54:09,959
I'm on a hurry.

622
00:54:22,709 --> 00:54:24,334
Hey! Hey! Guy!

623
00:54:24,751 --> 00:54:27,667
