646
00:55:16,584 --> 00:55:17,709
On a horse.

647
00:55:17,751 --> 00:55:20,250
Man, he's going to Mimoso
for sure. The Winter Festival.

648
00:55:20,250 --> 00:55:21,626
Filled with kids our age.

649
00:55:21,626 --> 00:55:23,125
Who knows, you just might
find him there.

650
00:55:23,167 --> 00:55:25,083
- He's in Mimoso for sure man.
