No problem.

668
00:56:06,626 --> 00:56:08,918
- Nobody is going to steal it, no way.
- I'm feeling bad.

669
00:56:08,918 --> 00:56:12,167
- So you just take it easy there.
- That's what I'm doing.

670
00:56:12,167 --> 00:56:14,918
- Don't hassle me.
- Are you OK?

671
00:56:14,959 --> 00:56:16,501
- He's feeling queasy.
- Poor thing.

672
00:56:16,542 --> 00:56:18,417
