00:56:18,459 --> 00:56:20,000
- You got chocolate man?
- Give it to me.

674
00:56:23,125 --> 00:56:24,250
It's my chocolate.

675
00:56:29,959 --> 00:56:31,250
Want some?

676
00:56:55,584 --> 00:56:57,459
Thanks a lot, man.

677
00:56:57,501 --> 00:56:59,000
Thanks a lot. Really.

