- I'd like to know that too.

723
01:00:05,959 --> 01:00:07,375
An insane trip.

724
01:00:08,375 --> 01:00:10,459
Is he around? Where is he?
Is he still here?

725
01:00:10,542 --> 01:00:11,876
He left.

726
01:00:14,292 --> 01:00:16,959
This one doesn't work.

727
01:00:18,292 --> 01:00:19,501
Have to take it to...

728
01:00:20,459 --> 01:00:22,250
- He's already gone?
- Yeah.

729
01:00:26,959 --> 01:00:28,292
Do you know where?

730
01:00:30,709 --> 01:00:33,709
He was in a hurry.
Said he couldn't stay.

731
01:00:34,876 --> 01:00:37,375
I even joked around with him.
I told him...

732
01:00:37,417 --> 01:00:39,876
